@baseUrl = http://localhost:5050
@adminToken = <paste_admin_jwt_here>
@passengerToken = <paste_passenger_jwt_here>

### ── Passenger (self-service) ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Get own profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/passengers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}

### Update own profile
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/public/passengers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Anna",
  "lastName": "Kowalska",
  "homeAddress": "ul. Nowy Świat 1, Warszawa",
  "preferredPaymentMethod": "CreditCard"
}

### Get loyalty points balance
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/public/passengers/me/loyalty-points
Authorization: Bearer {{passengerToken}}

### ── Admin ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List all passengers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/passengers?page=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Get single passenger
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/passengers/<passenger-id>
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
